      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without issue. While there may be some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the car is mechanically sound and ready for the road. It has been a reliable vehicle for us, and we have kept up with all recommended service intervals.",
